Class TeamMember

  • java.lang.Object
    • TeamMember

  • public class TeamMember
extends java.lang.Object
    A data structure holding the name and startDate of a TeamMember with basic functionality. Functionality includes read-only access of data, and equals() method, and a toString90 method.
